divs: Sighting Detailshaving a conversation about UFO's with a fellow i work with recently and he told about an event that happened at date specified above, near Los olivos california, santa barbara county. this was this guy's wedding reception so he knew exact date and time. lot of witnesses, including his father who, until he retired, was the pilot for the Governor of South Dakota. his father told my friend "what i saw can't be done by traditional aircraft." told my friend i would contact you and ask if you had similar reports on that date in that location.
